{"tid":1561164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所提出與倫敦交易所併購單嘢，大家定D黎","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T23:53:25.000Z","uid":139319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cda4fa0ed42ec131d5ca32f76abbf580c82bf7a5","tid":1561164,"uid":139319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"首先我哋睇睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ki7jJSz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKi7jJSz.png&h=82d9d6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBDyOjq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBDyOjq.png&h=3c850281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倫交所發行股數係349.74M股，港交所要付現金(349.74M*20.45)=7152M英鎊(71.52億鎊或692.8億港元)及發行872.6M 新股，相當於已發行股數69.36%或合併後總股數40.95%。<br />\n再睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KkA1Jq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KkA1Jq.png&h=5e0d8302&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWDyOou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWDyOou.png&h=3842db65&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n根據港交所今年中期報表，手頭現金97.75億，要應付692.8億港紙，必然要大舉集資。無非係黎個世紀大比例供股 + 發債 + 銀貸。(不過呢個係國家任務，撲水一定無問題。)<br />\n港交所出呢個價，以<span style=\"color: red;\">敵意收購黎講</span>，出手太低啦，只係溢價22.3%，你調返轉頭黎睇，如果有人出HKD300/股收購港交所，你係咪覺得好抵?。<br />\n港中係呢個時間出手，無非係因為以下原因：<br />\n一) 英鎊係硬脫歐危機下真係低水，9.7都無，美金咁強，而家出手可以慳返兌換200~300億港紙啦。<br />\n二) 趁英國政局不穩下，<span style=\"color: red;\">想乘人之危以低價收購</span>，然後拖英國落水，轉入中共陣營。英國咁識玩政治，大家放心就算過到倫交所股東(大部份都係機構投資者，咁嘅溢價收梗皮)，都過唔到英國嘅監管機構。<br />\n三)我覺得最大機會係班港中聯同大陸D權貴想趁機炒返轉港交所，食返次大茶飯。因為明知今次收購係99%會失敗，但都明知不可為而為之，咁就可以肯定有人想趁機掠水。<br />\n<br />\n***倫交所話適當時候會講點回應，估計都係話唔得。大家放心啦。"},{"pid":"5a21fb41c6f0a15ee12e2a367228bee31858ca22","tid":1561164,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0f727e7c72e92423d9488063fab0568707a1669d","tid":1561164,"uid":310898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"唔可以比佢得逞<br />\n<br />\n根本就好似當年想要返香港咁，用小恩小惠同英國買返債券。<br />\n<br />\n如果成功收購左，中國一樣拎住英國嘅春袋。<br />\n<br />\n重申，香港係屬於中華民國、或者屬於英國，或者係一個冇主權嘅獨立地區，視乎我哋之後想點爭取、點走下去"},{"pid":"ce6d3abec57fd6fceab13c5e49b9464ef3829f67","tid":1561164,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"fa90e64b17c38fd8be0041df9e96795d1344239a","tid":1561164,"uid":298225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:53:25.000Z","msg":"計埋數，幫你推下。"}]}